{"tid":2315054,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"黃榕放狗 被野狗遇襲爆缸","createTime":"2020-12-07T03:16:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T03:43:07.000Z","uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"65bfdbb1a57894bffe2531e611dc6a58f61e4489","tid":2315054,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T03:16:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/w_Aze2jBq2EuixRopO0LYQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTExMzcuNzc3Nzc3Nzc3Nzc3OA--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/A3rSf0KKiXHRx3mCATtk0A--~B/aD05NjA7dz01NDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/thesun.hk.com/9dbea36d895f93dc1272592908313743\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fw_Aze2jBq2EuixRopO0LYQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTExMzcuNzc3Nzc3Nzc3Nzc3OA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FA3rSf0KKiXHRx3mCATtk0A--~B%2FaD05NjA7dz01NDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fthesun.hk.com%2F9dbea36d895f93dc1272592908313743&h=b64ebed6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事發時，黃榕心急救愛犬，過程中自己亦被咬傷。<br />\n<br />\n藝人黃榕前日帶愛犬「妙妙」外出散步時發生意外，突然被野狗襲擊！她發文講述遇襲經過：「突然1秒間，不知那來人咁高的野狗衝過來咬我妙妙不放，我拉扯回妙妙，野狗1秒已經跑上很斜的山不見了，妙妙咁可愛，咬到佢爛晒。」<br />\n<br />\n黃榕的愛犬有4個傷口，需剃毛治理傷口及留院1晚，而她自己的手指亦淌血，需打破傷風針，不少網友都祝福她早日康復及找到「兇手」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/5w_cH1V1v6Poe1HYrIffbg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/thesun.hk.com/b73cd718462a060c9782883aa5b63041\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F5w_cH1V1v6Poe1HYrIffbg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fthesun.hk.com%2Fb73cd718462a060c9782883aa5b63041&h=c6137967&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃榕抱起受傷的「妙妙」急急求醫。"},{"pid":"d8b2b424b373f81ab44ab09c24f91a99f3c41acc","tid":2315054,"uid":331590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T03:21:08.000Z","msg":"新聞?"},{"pid":"